description:
I've teamed up with Pause and Beef once again, this time we are taking on Uncharted Territory 3, a CTM map by Amlup. The goal is to find all 16 wool colors and place these on the victory monument to finish the map.

PauseUnpause: http://www.youtube.com/PauseUnpause
VintageBeef: http://www.youtube.com/user/VintageBeef

Map By: Amlup
Map Download: http://www.minecraftforum.net/topic/1380417-amlups-uncharted-territory-series-ut3-released-for-162/
